Welcome to the timed-grid-test sample form!

This form demonstrates the functionality of the field plug-in through Early Grade Reading Assessment (EGRA) subtasks.

The first tests illustrate all available assessment types, using the default configuration settings: all-answered=999, page-rows=5, duration=60, end-after=5, strict=true, finish=3, pause=1.

Following this, we will test each parameter individually, using the Letters assessment type as the reference task.
